description:
Here's To Happy Endings: Jackie and Ben audition burlesque dancers for the looming La Mascara launch. Andrea shoots the cover of her yet-to-be released book, The Working Mother's Revenge. Cancer survivor Gina hosts a Girls Night In fundraising evening in aid of cancer research. She doesn't invite Andrea who wouldn't come anyway. Chyka encourages Gina and Andrea to meet and discuss their differences but are they ready to be civil before the big La Mascara launch party?
If you see "Hector" on the end of a file it means I capped it.
Enjoy, Gaz/Hector :)
